\u001b[0m都会看到同一个分支\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m正确的方式\u001b[0m是使用 TermCanvas 的 worktree 功能：\r\n  - 在一个项目上右键 → \"Add Worktree\" → 选择分支\r\n  - 这会创建一个独立目录的 worktree\r\n  - 在新的 worktree 里开的终端，完全隔离，不受其他分支影响\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m检查你的项目有没有多个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在项目根目录运行：\r\n  git worktree list\r\n\r\n  如果你只看到一个路径，说明你还没有创建额外的 worktree，所有分支切换都在同一个目录里互相覆盖。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1m另外你问我觉得这个项目质量怎么样？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87;22m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102m Searched for \u001b[1m2\u001b[22m patterns, read \u001b[1m2\u001b[22m files (ctrl+o to expand)     \r\n\u001b[22C     \r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m●\u001b[1C\u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n \u001b[38;2;171;43;63m \u001b[27C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mTermCanvas 目前没有创建 worktree 的功能\r\n\u001b[94C\u001b[0m             虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\u001b[31C\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m \u001b[0m             \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[1C\u001b[0m在\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\u001b[1C\u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\u001b[5C           \r\n\u001b[93C\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m \u001b[0m           \r\n  这意味着：      \u001b[76C \u001b[1C         \r\n                                                                                                           1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mlist\u001b[0m 的结果会自动同步到 UI                         \r\n\u001b[2C2.\u001b[1C\u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1C的\u001b[1CUI\u001b[1C或命令\u001b[1C\u001b[0m—\u001b[1C你必须手动用\u001b[1Cgit\u001b[1C命令创建\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mSearched for \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m pattern, read \u001b[1m2\u001b[22m files (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree 并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree\r\n  目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m2\u001b[22m files (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree 并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree\r\n  目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m等端点，然后在 UI\r\n  里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Cogitated for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n \u001b[38;2;102;102;102m Read \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)    \r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m●\u001b[1C\u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到\u001b[1CGitHub\u001b[1C的\u001b[1Cissue：\r\n \u001b[38;2;255;153;51m \r\n\u001b[0m  ---\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1mIssue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees\u001b[0m          \r\n\u001b[93C\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m \u001b[0m             TermCanvas\u001b[1Cuses\u001b[1Creal\u001b[1Cgit\u001b[1Cworktrees\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Callow\u001b[1Cmultiple\u001b[1Cbranches\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Ccoexist\u001b[1Cin\u001b[1Cthe\u001b[1Csame\u001b[1Cproject without     interfering with each other's terminals. The existing worktrees are automatically detected and         \r\n  displayed correctly,\u001b[1Cbut\u001b[1Cthere\u001b[1Cis\u001b[1Cno\u001b[1Cway\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Ccreate\u001b[1Cnew\u001b[1Cworktrees\u001b[1Cor\u001b[1Cremove\u001b[1Cexisting\u001b[1Cones\u001b[1Cfrom\u001b[1Cwithin   \r\n\u001b[2Cthe\u001b[1Capp.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \u001b[0mand \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and      \r\n  TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that \r\n  worktree's directory and are unaffected by operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas. There is no context menu  \r\n  item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that attempts to call\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist \r\n  in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually\r\n   in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch) directly from TermCanvas,    \r\n  without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for different branches never  \r\n  interfere with each other.\r\n                                                                                                         \u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  to add worktrees      就这样？                                                                           \u001b[0m                                                                                                         \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd UI and API to create/delete git worktrees within TermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While     existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or    remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints     (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in                         \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\u001b[94C           \r\n\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── \u001b[0m           \r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m2\u001b[22m files (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree 并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree\r\n  目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m等端点，然后在 UI\r\n  里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Cogitated for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in the same project without   \r\n  interfering with each other's terminals. The existing worktrees are automatically detected and\r\n  displayed correctly, but there is no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within   \r\n  the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \u001b[0mand \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and      \r\n  TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that \r\n  worktree's directory and are unaffected by operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas. There is no context menu  \r\n  item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that attempts to call\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist \r\n  in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually\r\n   in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch) directly from TermCanvas,    \r\n  without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for different branches never  \r\n  interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mto add worktrees      就这样？                                                                           \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree 并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree\r\n  目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m等端点，然后在 UI\r\n  里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Cogitated for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;