55m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist \r\n  in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually\r\n   in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch) directly from TermCanvas,    \r\n  without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for different branches never  \r\n  interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mto add worktrees      就这样？                                                                           \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                                                    \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                        \u001b[18X\u001b[18C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m●\u001b[38;2;255;153;51m \u001b[39;1mDescribe the bug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees\u001b[1Cfrom\u001b[1Cwithin\u001b[1Cthe\u001b[1Capp.\u001b[1CThe\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage\u001b[1C\u001b[0magent\r\n\u001b[2Ctool\u001b[1Cis\u001b[1Cimplemented\u001b[1Cand\u001b[1Creferences\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m,\u001b[1Cand\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[1C\u001b[0mAPI            endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add\u001b[1C\u001b[0min\u001b[1Can\u001b[1Cexternal\u001b[1Cterminal\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Ccreate\u001b[1Ca\u001b[1Cnew\u001b[1Cbranch/worktree,\u001b[1Cbreaking\u001b[1Cthe\u001b[1Cmulti-branch          workflow inside TermCanvas.\u001b[55C\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m \u001b[0m           \r\n  \u001b[92C \u001b[1C         \r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1mSteps\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Creproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree 并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree\r\n  目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m等端点，然后在 UI\r\n  里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Cogitated for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in the same project without   \r\n  interfering with each other's terminals. The existing worktrees are automatically detected and\r\n  displayed correctly, but there is no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within   \r\n  the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \u001b[0mand \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and      \r\n  TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that \r\n  worktree's directory and are unaffected by operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas. There is no context menu  \r\n  item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that attempts to call\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist \r\n  in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually\r\n   in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch) directly from TermCanvas,    \r\n  without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for different branches never  \r\n  interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mto add worktrees      就这样？                                                                           \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                                                    \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                                                      \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.\u001b[70X\u001b[70C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent  \r\n  tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the multi-branch        \r\n  workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API endpoints and fails silently \r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\u001b[94C\u001b[0m           \u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[90X\r\n\u001b[94C           \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m●\u001b[38;2;255;153;51m \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage\u001b[1C\u001b[0mtool\u001b[1C调用了不存在的\u001b[1CAPI，那就是\u001b[1Cbug。\u001b[30C\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m \u001b[0m           \r\n\u001b[94C             ---\u001b[89C             \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent tool calls non-existent \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI endpoints\u001b[17C\u001b[0m           \r\n\u001b[93C\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m \u001b[0m           \r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage\u001b[1C\u001b[0mtool\u001b[1Cin\u001b[1Cthe\u001b[1Cagent\u001b[1Ccalls\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m,\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\u001b[1Cand\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove    \u001b[0m  \r\n\u001b[2Cendpoints,\u001b[1Cbut\u001b[1Cnone\u001b[1Cof\u001b[1Cthese\u001b[1Care\u001b[1Cimplemented\u001b[1Cin\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m.\u001b[1CThe\u001b[1Ctool\u001b[1Calways\u001b[1Cfails,\u001b[1Cand\r\n  there is no UI to create or remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n✻ Cogitated for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in the same project without   \r\n  interfering with each other's terminals. The existing worktrees are automatically detected and\r\n  displayed correctly, but there is no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within   \r\n  the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \u001b[0mand \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and      \r\n  TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that \r\n  worktree's directory and are unaffected by operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas. There is no context menu  \r\n  item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that attempts to call\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist \r\n  in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually\r\n   in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch) directly from TermCanvas,    \r\n  without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for different branches never  \r\n  interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mto add worktrees      就这样？                                                                           \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                                                    \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                                                      \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.               \u001b[47X\u001b[47C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent  \r\n  tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the multi-branch        \r\n  workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API endpoints and fails silently \r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove      \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and     \r\n  there is no UI to create or remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in the same project without   \r\n  interfering with each other's terminals. The existing worktrees are automatically detected and\r\n  displayed correctly, but there is no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within   \r\n  the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \u001b[0mand \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and      \r\n  TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that \r\n  worktree's directory and are unaffected by operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas. There is no context menu  \r\n  item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that attempts to call\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist \r\n  in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually\r\n   in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch) directly from TermCanvas,    \r\n  without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for different branches never  \r\n  interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mto add worktrees      就这样？                                                                           \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                                                    \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                                                      \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent  \r\n  tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the multi-branch        \r\n  workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API endpoints and fails silently \r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove      \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and     \r\n  there is no UI to create or remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in the same project without   \r\n  interfering with each other's terminals. The existing worktrees are automatically detected and\r\n  displayed correctly, but there is no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within   \r\n  the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \u001b[0mand \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and      \r\n  TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that \r\n  worktree's directory and are unaffected by operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas. There is no context menu  \r\n  item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that attempts to call\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist \r\n  in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually\r\n   in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch) directly from TermCanvas,    \r\n  without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for different branches never  \r\n  interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mto add worktrees      就这样？                                                                           \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                                                    \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                                                      \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees\u001b[1Cfrom\u001b[1Cwithin\u001b[1Cthe\u001b[1Capp.\u001b[1CThe\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage\u001b[1C\u001b[0magent\r\n  tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the multi-branch        \r\n  workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API endpoints and fails silently \r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove      \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and     \r\n  there is no UI to create or remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in the same project without   \r\n  interfering with each other's terminals. The existing worktrees are automatically detected and\r\n  displayed correctly, but there is no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within   \r\n  the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \u001b[0mand \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and      \r\n  TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that \r\n  worktree's directory and are unaffected by operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas. There is no context menu  \r\n  item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that attempts to call\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist \r\n  in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually\r\n   in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch) directly from TermCanvas,    \r\n  without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for different branches never  \r\n  interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mto add worktrees      就这样？                                                                           \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                                                    \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                                                      \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m  \r\n\u001b[0m  tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the multi-branch        \r\n  workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API endpoints and fails silently \r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove      \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and     \r\n  there is no UI to create or remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or the tool should be removed \r\n  if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)       \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within TermCanvas — no UI or command  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mto add worktrees      就这样？\u001b[63X\u001b[63C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.\u001b[54X\u001b[54C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m\u001b[93X\u001b[93C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...\u001b[87X\u001b[87C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...\u001b[87X\u001b[87C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                                                   \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                                                    \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                                                      \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent  \r\n  tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the multi-branch        \r\n  workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API endpoints and fails silently \r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\u001b[1Cand\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and     \r\n  there is no UI to create or remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or the tool should be removed \r\n  if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)       \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API endpoints是什么意思\u001b[6X\u001b[6C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code 可以调用它来管理 git worktree）    \r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个 API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove    \r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API endpoints   \r\n  (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an       \r\n  external terminal to create a new branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add worktree\" on a project, or a  \r\n  slash command), so all multi-branch workflow stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.\u001b[54X\u001b[54C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m\u001b[93X\u001b[93C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...\u001b[87X\u001b[87C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...\u001b[87X\u001b[87C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...\u001b[87X\u001b[87C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m\u001b[93X\u001b[93C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**\u001b[72X\u001b[72C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                                                      \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                                         \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                                          \u001b[0m\u001b[95X\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent  \r\n  tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the multi-branch        \r\n  workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API endpoints and fails silently \r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove      \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and     \r\n  there is no UI to create or remove git\u001b[1Cworktrees\u001b[1Cfrom\u001b[1Cwithin\u001b[1CTermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or the tool should be removed \r\n  if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)       \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API endpoints是什么意思\u001b[6X\u001b[6C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code 可以调用它来管理 git worktree）    \r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个 API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove    \r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.\u001b[54X\u001b[54C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m\u001b[93X\u001b[93C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...\u001b[87X\u001b[87C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...\u001b[87X\u001b[87C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...\u001b[87X\u001b[87C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m\u001b[93X\u001b[93C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**\u001b[72X\u001b[72C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.\u001b[65X\u001b[65C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m\u001b[93X\u001b[93C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**\u001b[74X\u001b[74C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.\u001b[70X\u001b[70C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m\u001b[93X\u001b[93C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]\u001b[70X\u001b[70C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]\u001b[68X\u001b[68C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m\u001b[93X\u001b[93C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent  \r\n  tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit     \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the multi-branch        \r\n  workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals in each worktree are      \r\n  properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command, button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API endpoints and fails silently \r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove      \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and     \r\n  there is no UI to create or remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or the tool should be removed \r\n  if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)       \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API endpoints是什么意思\u001b[6X\u001b[6C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code 可以调用它来管理 git worktree）    \r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个 API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove    \r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree\r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[66X\u001b[66C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove      \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails with a   \r\n  404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or the tool should be removed \r\n  if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals. While   \r\n  existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or  \r\n  remove existing ones without leaving the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas      \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌\u001b[3C\u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[1CCode\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102;22mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘\u001b[2C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7\u001b[1C·\u001b[1CAPI\u001b[1CUsage\u001b[1CBilling\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m \u001b[1C▘▘\u001b[1C▝▝\u001b[4C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[2CRead\u001b[1C\u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file\u001b[1C(ctrl+o\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Cexpand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m●\u001b[1C\u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[1C目前没有创建\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1C的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m虽然代码里有\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent\u001b[1C工具），但它调用的\u001b[1CAPI\u001b[1C端点\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[1C\u001b[0m在\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C这意味着：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C1.\u001b[1C\u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[1C能显示已有的\u001b[1Cworktrees\u001b[1C\u001b[0m—\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1Clist\u001b[1C\u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到\u001b[1CUI\r\n\u001b[2C2.\u001b[1C\u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1C的\u001b[1CUI\u001b[1C或命令\u001b[1C\u001b[0m—\u001b[1C你必须手动用\u001b[1Cgit\u001b[1C命令创建\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m在\u001b[1CTermCanvas\u001b[1C的终端里手动创建\u001b[1Cworktree：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C#\u001b[1C在你的项目根目录执行\r\n  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree\r\n  并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree 目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create    \r\n\u001b[0m  等端点，然后在 UI 里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Worked for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m  \r\n  \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in   \r\n  the same project without interfering with each other's terminals. The existing\r\n   worktrees are automatically detected and displayed correctly, but there is no\r\n   way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within the app.     \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \r\n\u001b[0m  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.    \r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in     \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that worktree's directory and are unaffected by       \r\n  operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas.  \r\n  There is no context menu item, no slash command, and no button for it.        \r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that        \r\n  attempts to call \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI   \r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the \r\n  tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch)     \r\n  directly from TermCanvas, without needing an external terminal. For example:  \r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name   \r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for  \r\n  different branches never interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mTermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees      就这样？                    \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n  displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones  \r\n  without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API\r\n  endpoints (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not   \r\n  implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must   \r\n  manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new\r\n  branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add      \r\n  worktree\" on a project, or a slash command), so all multi-branch workflow     \r\n  stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                           \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                    \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                              \u001b[39m   \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                              \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app.  \r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not\r\n   exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min \r\n  an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the\r\n  multi-branch workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals  \r\n  in each worktree are properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command,   \r\n  button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches)      \r\n  directly from TermCanvas without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees      \r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API     \r\n  endpoints and fails silently\r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m        \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and there is no UI to create or\r\n   remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in      \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API\u001b[26X\u001b[26C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mendpoints是什么意思                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code\r\n  可以调用它来管理 git worktree）\r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个\r\n  API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree \r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[66X\u001b[66C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m      \r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m  \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails with a 404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m     \r\n\r\n  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌\u001b[3C\u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[1CCode\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102;22mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘\u001b[2C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7\u001b[1C·\u001b[1CAPI\u001b[1CUsage\u001b[1CBilling\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m \u001b[1C▘▘\u001b[1C▝▝\u001b[4C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[2CRead\u001b[1C\u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file\u001b[1C(ctrl+o\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Cexpand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m●\u001b[1C\u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[1C目前没有创建\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1C的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m虽然代码里有\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent\u001b[1C工具），但它调用的\u001b[1CAPI\u001b[1C端点\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[1C\u001b[0m在\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C这意味着：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C1.\u001b[1C\u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[1C能显示已有的\u001b[1Cworktrees\u001b[1C\u001b[0m—\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1Clist\u001b[1C\u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到\u001b[1CUI\r\n\u001b[2C2.\u001b[1C\u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1C的\u001b[1CUI\u001b[1C或命令\u001b[1C\u001b[0m—\u001b[1C你必须手动用\u001b[1Cgit\u001b[1C命令创建\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m在\u001b[1CTermCanvas\u001b[1C的终端里手动创建\u001b[1Cworktree：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C#\u001b[1C在你的项目根目录执行\r\n  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree\r\n  并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree 目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create    \r\n\u001b[0m  等端点，然后在 UI 里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Worked for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m  \r\n  \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in   \r\n  the same project without interfering with each other's terminals. The existing\r\n   worktrees are automatically detected and displayed correctly, but there is no\r\n   way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within the app.     \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \r\n\u001b[0m  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.    \r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in     \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that worktree's directory and are unaffected by       \r\n  operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas.  \r\n  There is no context menu item, no slash command, and no button for it.        \r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that        \r\n  attempts to call \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI   \r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the \r\n  tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch)     \r\n  directly from TermCanvas, without needing an external terminal. For example:  \r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name   \r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for  \r\n  different branches never interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mTermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees      就这样？                    \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n  displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones  \r\n  without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API\r\n  endpoints (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not   \r\n  implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must   \r\n  manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new\r\n  branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add      \r\n  worktree\" on a project, or a slash command), so all multi-branch workflow     \r\n  stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                           \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                    \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                              \u001b[39m   \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                              \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app.  \r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not\r\n   exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min \r\n  an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the\r\n  multi-branch workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals  \r\n  in each worktree are properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command,   \r\n  button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches)      \r\n  directly from TermCanvas without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees      \r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API     \r\n  endpoints and fails silently\r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m        \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and there is no UI to create or\r\n   remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in      \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API\u001b[26X\u001b[26C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mendpoints是什么意思                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code\r\n  可以调用它来管理 git worktree）\r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个\r\n  API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree \r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[66X\u001b[66C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m      \r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m  \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails with a 404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m     \r\n\r\n  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\r\n\u001b[0m  里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree\r\n  并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree 目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create    \r\n\u001b[0m  等端点，然后在 UI 里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Worked for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m  \r\n  \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in   \r\n  the same project without interfering with each other's terminals. The existing\r\n   worktrees are automatically detected and displayed correctly, but there is no\r\n   way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within the app.     \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \r\n\u001b[0m  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.    \r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in     \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that worktree's directory and are unaffected by       \r\n  operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas.  \r\n  There is no context menu item, no slash command, and no button for it.        \r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that        \r\n  attempts to call \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI   \r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the \r\n  tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch)     \r\n  directly from TermCanvas, without needing an external terminal. For example:  \r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name   \r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for  \r\n  different branches never interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mTermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees      就这样？                    \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n  displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones  \r\n  without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API\r\n  endpoints (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not   \r\n  implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must   \r\n  manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new\r\n  branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add      \r\n  worktree\" on a project, or a slash command), so all multi-branch workflow     \r\n  stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                           \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                    \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                    \u001b[42X\u001b[42C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                              \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app.  \r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not\r\n   exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min \r\n  an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the\r\n  multi-branch workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals  \r\n  in each worktree are properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command,   \r\n  button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches)      \r\n  directly from TermCanvas without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees      \r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API     \r\n  endpoints and fails silently\r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m        \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and there is no UI to create or\r\n   remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in      \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API\u001b[26X\u001b[26C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mendpoints是什么意思                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code\r\n  可以调用它来管理 git worktree）\r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个\r\n  API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree \r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[66X\u001b[66C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m      \r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m  \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails with a 404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m     \r\n\r\n  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌\u001b[3C\u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[1CCode\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102;22mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘\u001b[2C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7\u001b[1C·\u001b[1CAPI\u001b[1CUsage\u001b[1CBilling\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m \u001b[1C▘▘\u001b[1C▝▝\u001b[4C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[2CRead\u001b[1C\u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file\u001b[1C(ctrl+o\u001b[1Cto\u001b[1Cexpand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m●\u001b[1C\u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[1C目前没有创建\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1C的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m虽然代码里有\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent\u001b[1C工具），但它调用的\u001b[1CAPI\u001b[1C端点\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[1C\u001b[0m在\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C这意味着：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C1.\u001b[1C\u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[1C能显示已有的\u001b[1Cworktrees\u001b[1C\u001b[0m—\u001b[1C\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1Clist\u001b[1C\u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到\u001b[1CUI\r\n\u001b[2C2.\u001b[1C\u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[1Cworktree\u001b[1C的\u001b[1CUI\u001b[1C或命令\u001b[1C\u001b[0m—\u001b[1C你必须手动用\u001b[1Cgit\u001b[1C命令创建\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C\u001b[0m在\u001b[1CTermCanvas\u001b[1C的终端里手动创建\u001b[1Cworktree：\r\n\r\n\u001b[2C#\u001b[1C在你的项目根目录执行\r\n  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree\r\n  并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree 目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create    \r\n\u001b[0m  等端点，然后在 UI 里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Baked for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m  \r\n  \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in   \r\n  the same project without interfering with each other's terminals. The existing\r\n   worktrees are automatically detected and displayed correctly, but there is no\r\n   way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within the app.     \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \r\n\u001b[0m  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.    \r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in     \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that worktree's directory and are unaffected by       \r\n  operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas.  \r\n  There is no context menu item, no slash command, and no button for it.        \r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that        \r\n  attempts to call \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI   \r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the \r\n  tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch)     \r\n  directly from TermCanvas, without needing an external terminal. For example:  \r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name   \r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for  \r\n  different branches never interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mTermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees      就这样？                    \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n  displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones  \r\n  without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API\r\n  endpoints (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not   \r\n  implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must   \r\n  manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new\r\n  branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add      \r\n  worktree\" on a project, or a slash command), so all multi-branch workflow     \r\n  stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                           \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                    \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                               \u001b[39m  \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                              \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app.  \r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not\r\n   exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min \r\n  an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the\r\n  multi-branch workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals  \r\n  in each worktree are properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command,   \r\n  button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches)      \r\n  directly from TermCanvas without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees      \r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API     \r\n  endpoints and fails silently\r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m        \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and there is no UI to create or\r\n   remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in      \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API\u001b[26X\u001b[26C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mendpoints是什么意思                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code\r\n  可以调用它来管理 git worktree）\r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个\r\n  API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree \r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[66X\u001b[66C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m      \r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m  \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails with a 404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints\u001b[1Cdon't\u001b[1Cexist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m     \r\n\r\n  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\r\n\u001b[0m  里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree\r\n  并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree 目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create    \r\n\u001b[0m  等端点，然后在 UI 里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Baked for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[43X\u001b[43C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\u001b[0m  \r\n  \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in   \r\n  the same project without interfering with each other's terminals. The existing\r\n   worktrees are automatically detected and displayed correctly, but there is no\r\n   way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within the app.     \r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain \r\n\u001b[0m  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.    \r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in     \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that worktree's directory and are unaffected by       \r\n  operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas.  \r\n  There is no context menu item, no slash command, and no button for it.        \r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that        \r\n  attempts to call \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI   \r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the \r\n  tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch)     \r\n  directly from TermCanvas, without needing an external terminal. For example:  \r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name   \r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for  \r\n  different branches never interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mTermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees      就这样？                    \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n  displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones  \r\n  without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API\r\n  endpoints (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not   \r\n  implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must   \r\n  manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new\r\n  branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add      \r\n  worktree\" on a project, or a slash command), so all multi-branch workflow     \r\n  stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[71X\u001b[71C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                           \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                    \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                     \u001b[41X\u001b[41C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                              \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app.  \r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not\r\n   exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min \r\n  an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the\r\n  multi-branch workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals  \r\n  in each worktree are properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command,   \r\n  button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches)      \r\n  directly from TermCanvas without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees      \r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API     \r\n  endpoints and fails silently\r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[78X\u001b[78C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m        \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and there is no UI to create or\r\n   remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in      \r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[62X\u001b[62C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API\u001b[26X\u001b[26C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mendpoints是什么意思                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code\r\n  可以调用它来管理 git worktree）\r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个\r\n  API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[59X\u001b[59C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree \r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[66X\u001b[66C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m   \r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m      \r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m  \r\n\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,  \r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails with a 404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch        \r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the\u001b[1CAPI\u001b[1Cendpoints\u001b[1Cdon't\u001b[1Cexist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or   \r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m     \r\n\r\n  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with    \r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and       \r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\r\n\u001b[0m  里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree\r\n  并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree 目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\r\n\u001b[0m  等端点，然后在 UI 里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Baked for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[30X\u001b[30C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in\r\n  the same project without interfering with each other's terminals. The existing\r\n   worktrees are automatically detected and displayed correctly, but there is no\r\n   way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\r\n\u001b[0m  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that worktree's directory and are unaffected by\r\n  operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas.\r\n  There is no context menu item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that\r\n  attempts to call \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the\r\n  tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch)\r\n  directly from TermCanvas, without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for\r\n  different branches never interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mTermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees      就这样？                    \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with\r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and\r\n  displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones\r\n  without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API\r\n  endpoints (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not\r\n  implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must\r\n  manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new\r\n  branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add\r\n  worktree\" on a project, or a slash command), so all multi-branch workflow\r\n  stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[58X\u001b[58C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                           \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                    \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                     \u001b[28X\u001b[28C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                              \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app.\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not\r\n   exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min\r\n  an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the\r\n  multi-branch workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals\r\n  in each worktree are properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command,\r\n  button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches)\r\n  directly from TermCanvas without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API\r\n  endpoints and fails silently\r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[65X\u001b[65C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[65X\u001b[65C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and there is no UI to create or\r\n   remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch\r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or\r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[49X\u001b[49C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API\u001b[13X\u001b[13C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mendpoints是什么意思                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code\r\n  可以调用它来管理 git worktree）\r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个\r\n  API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[46X\u001b[46C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree\r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[53X\u001b[53C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails with\r\n   a 404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or the tool should be    \r\n  removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals.    \r\n  While existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new    \r\n  worktrees or remove existing ones without leaving the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from Term\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\r\n\u001b[0m  里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree\r\n  并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree 目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\r\n\u001b[0m  等端点，然后在 UI 里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Baked for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[30X\u001b[30C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in\r\n  the same project without interfering with each other's terminals. The existing\r\n   worktrees are automatically detected and displayed correctly, but there is no\r\n   way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\r\n\u001b[0m  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that worktree's directory and are unaffected by\r\n  operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas.\r\n  There is no context menu item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that\r\n  attempts to call \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the\r\n  tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch)\r\n  directly from TermCanvas, without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for\r\n  different branches never interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mTermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees      就这样？                    \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with\r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and\r\n  displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones\r\n  without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API\r\n  endpoints (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not\r\n  implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must\r\n  manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new\r\n  branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add\r\n  worktree\" on a project, or a slash command), so all multi-branch workflow\r\n  stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[58X\u001b[58C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                           \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                    \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]\u001b[57X\u001b[57C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                              \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app.\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not\r\n   exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min\r\n  an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the\r\n  multi-branch workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals\r\n  in each worktree are properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command,\r\n  button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches)\r\n  directly from TermCanvas without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API\r\n  endpoints and fails silently\r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[65X\u001b[65C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[65X\u001b[65C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and there is no UI to create or\r\n   remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch\r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or\r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[49X\u001b[49C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API\u001b[13X\u001b[13C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mendpoints是什么意思                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code\r\n  可以调用它来管理 git worktree）\r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个\r\n  API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[46X\u001b[46C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree\r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[53X\u001b[53C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m.   \r\n  The tool always fails with a 404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or the tool should\r\n   be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated        \r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m ▐\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m▛███▜\u001b[49m▌   \u001b[39;1mClaude\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mv2.1.89\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m▝▜\u001b[48;2;0;0;0m█████\u001b[49m▛▘  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mMiniMax-M2.7 · API Usage Billing\r\n\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m  ▘▘ ▝▝    \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mD:\\coding\\Archive_Source_code\\termcanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m我查了一下，发现一个关键问题：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m目前没有创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  虽然代码里有 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m（Agent 工具），但它调用的 API 端点\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0m在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts\r\n\u001b[0m  里\u001b[1m根本不存在\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  这意味着：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m能显示已有的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0m的结果会自动同步到 UI\r\n  2. \u001b[1m但没有创建/删除\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m或命令\u001b[0m — 你必须手动用 git 命令创建\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m你现在能怎么做\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  在 TermCanvas 的终端里手动创建 worktree：\r\n\r\n  \u001b[32m# 在你的项目根目录执行\r\n\u001b[0m  git worktree add ../my-feature-branch feature-branch\r\n\r\n  创建完之后，TermCanvas 会自动扫描到新的 worktree\r\n  并显示在侧边栏。之后你可以在新的 worktree 目录里开终端，完全隔离。\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1m如果你想在\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m里直接创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  这是个功能缺失。你需要：\r\n  1. 在现有终端里用 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0m创建\r\n  2. 或者我可以帮你实现这个功能 — 需要在 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mapi-server.ts \u001b[0m里加 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\r\n\u001b[0m  等端点，然后在 UI 里加上对应的操作入口\r\n\r\n  要我帮你加上这个功能吗？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m✻ Baked for 1m 45s\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m我不自己写了 我给作者提一个issue吧 你写一下issue\u001b[30X\u001b[30C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102mRead \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m file (ctrl+o to expand)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m以下是你可以提交到 GitHub 的 issue：\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mIssue:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCannot\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mfrom\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mno\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mor\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcommand\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1madd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to allow multiple branches to coexist in\r\n  the same project without interfering with each other's terminals. The existing\r\n   worktrees are automatically detected and displayed correctly, but there is no\r\n   way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones from within the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mObserved\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Running \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree list \u001b[0min a project shows multiple worktrees (e.g. \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\r\n\u001b[0m  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x\u001b[0m), and TermCanvas displays them all correctly in the sidebar.\r\n  2. Terminals opened in each worktree are properly isolated — terminals in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mfeature-x \u001b[0mare rooted in that worktree's directory and are unaffected by\r\n  operations in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mmain\u001b[0m.\r\n  3. However, there is no way to create a new worktree from within TermCanvas.\r\n  There is no context menu item, no slash command, and no button for it.\r\n  4. The Claude Code agent has a \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool\u001b[0m) that\r\n  attempts to call \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI\r\n  endpoints, but these endpoints do not exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, so the\r\n  tool cannot actually manage worktrees.\r\n  5. To create a new branch/worktree today, users must leave TermCanvas and run\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0mmanually in an external terminal.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior:\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create a new git worktree (and thus a new branch)\r\n  directly from TermCanvas, without needing an external terminal. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project or worktree → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  This would allow truly isolated multi-branch development where terminals for\r\n  different branches never interfere with each other.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m能不能用正规一点的title  Issue: Cannot create git worktrees from within       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mTermCanvas — no UI or command to add worktrees      就这样？                    \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with\r\n  isolated terminals. While existing worktrees are correctly detected and\r\n  displayed, users have no way to create new worktrees or remove existing ones\r\n  without leaving the app. The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool references API\r\n  endpoints (\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\u001b[0m) that are not\r\n  implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m, making it non-functional. Users must\r\n  manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min an external terminal to create a new\r\n  branch/worktree.\r\n\r\n  Expected: a built-in way to add/remove worktrees (e.g. context menu \"Add\r\n  worktree\" on a project, or a slash command), so all multi-branch workflow\r\n  stays within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m**Describe the bug**\u001b[58X\u001b[58C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mA clear description of what the bug is.                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Steps to reproduce**                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m1. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m2. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m3. ...                                                                          \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Expected behavior**                                                           \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat you expected to happen.                                                    \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Actual behavior**                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mWhat actually happened.                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Environment**                                     \u001b[28X\u001b[28C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- OS: [e.g. macOS 15.0]                                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- Node.js: [e.g. 20.10.0]                                                       \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m- TermCanvas version: [e.g. 0.1.0]                                              \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[48;2;220;220;220m                                                                                \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220m**Screenshots**                                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mIf applicable, add screenshots.                                                 \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mDescribe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mthe\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbug\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas has no way to create or remove git worktrees from within the app.\r\n  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0magent tool is implemented and references \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mAPI endpoints, but these endpoints do not\r\n   exist in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. Users must manually run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add \u001b[0min\r\n  an external terminal to create a new branch/worktree, breaking the\r\n  multi-branch workflow inside TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas that has multiple branches\r\n  2. Observe that all existing worktrees are displayed correctly and terminals\r\n  in each worktree are properly isolated\r\n  3. Try to find a way to create a new worktree (context menu, slash command,\r\n  button, etc.)\r\n  4. No such option exists\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches)\r\n  directly from TermCanvas without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  - No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees\r\n  - The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the Claude Code agent calls non-existent API\r\n  endpoints and fails silently\r\n  - Users must use an external terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m生成一个title\u001b[65X\u001b[65C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1min-app\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreation\u001b[0m \u001b[1mand\u001b[0m \u001b[1mdeletion\u001b[0m \u001b[1m(API\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\u001b[0m \u001b[1m+\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI)\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m这应该是bug吧\u001b[65X\u001b[65C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对，既然 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool 调用了不存在的 API，那就是 bug。\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m,\r\n  and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \u001b[0mendpoints, but none of these are implemented in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails, and there is no UI to create or\r\n   remove git worktrees from within TermCanvas.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch\r\n  feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or\r\n  the tool should be removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found (API route does not exist in\r\n  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m)\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m那title呢 应该这样： Bug：xxx\u001b[49X\u001b[49C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220;22m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0mBug: WorktreeManage agent tool calls non-existent /worktree/* API\u001b[13X\u001b[13C\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0;48;2;220;220;220mendpoints是什么意思                                                             \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m意思是：\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m是 TermCanvas 里内置的一个 \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具\u001b[0m（Claude Code\r\n  可以调用它来管理 git worktree）\r\n  - 这个工具在代码里已经写好了，它会调用 3 个\r\n  API：\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m、\u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove\r\n\u001b[0m  - 但实际上 \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts \u001b[0m里\u001b[1m根本没有实现这几个\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m路由\r\n\u001b[0m  - 所以工具一调用就 404报错，根本用不了\r\n\r\n  换句话说：\u001b[1m功能做了但没做完，后端接口是空的\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m啊？但是不是前端也没做这个功能吗\u001b[46X\u001b[46C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[0m对的，你说得更准确。\r\n\r\n  完整缺失的部分：\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[1mAgent\u001b[0m \u001b[1m工具的\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1m是空的\u001b[0m — \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mworktreeTool \u001b[0m代码写好了，但后端没实现\r\n  2. \u001b[1mApp\u001b[0m \u001b[1m本身也没有\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m — 没有右键菜单、没有按钮、没有 slash 命令来创建 worktree\r\n\r\n  所以不只是\"做了一半没完成\"的问题，是\u001b[1m整个创建\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktree\u001b[0m \u001b[1m的功能都没有\u001b[0m。\r\n\r\n  你觉得要提哪个：\r\n  - \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m: \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0m工具调用的 API 不存在\r\n  - \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m: 需要一个在 App 内创建/删除 worktree 的功能\r\n\r\n  还是两个都写进去？\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;175;175;175;48;2;220;220;220m> \u001b[38;2;0;0;0m都写？Bug&Feature Request\u001b[53X\u001b[53C\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[38;2;0;0;0m● \u001b[39;1mBug:\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest:\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mBug\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1mWorktreeManage \u001b[39magent\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtool\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcalls\u001b[0m \u001b[1mnon-existent\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;51;102;255;1m/worktree/* \u001b[39mAPI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mendpoints\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  The \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool in the agent calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/list\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create\u001b[0m, and \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/remove \r\n\u001b[0m  endpoints, but none of these are implemented in \u001b[38;2;51;102;255melectron/api-server.ts\u001b[0m. The tool always fails with\r\n   a 404.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mSteps\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mreproduce\r\n\u001b[0m  1. Open a project in TermCanvas\r\n  2. Use the \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool (e.g. \"create a new worktree for branch feature-x\")\r\n  3. The tool returns an error because the API endpoints don't exist\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mWorktreeManage \u001b[0mtool should work, or the endpoints should be implemented, or the tool should be    \r\n  removed if unsupported.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Tool calls \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree/create \u001b[0m→ 404 Not Found\r\n\r\n  ---\r\n  \u001b[1mFeature\u001b[0m \u001b[1mRequest\u001b[0m \u001b[1m—\u001b[0m \u001b[1mAdd\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUI\u001b[0m \u001b[1mto\u001b[0m \u001b[1mcreate/delete\u001b[0m \u001b[1mgit\u001b[0m \u001b[1mworktrees\u001b[0m \u001b[1mwithin\u001b[0m \u001b[1mTermCanvas\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  TermCanvas uses real git worktrees to enable multi-branch development with isolated terminals.    \r\n  While existing worktrees are correctly detected and displayed, users have no way to create new    \r\n  worktrees or remove existing ones without leaving the app.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mExpected\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  Users should be able to create new git worktrees (and thus new branches) directly from TermCanvas \r\n  without leaving the app. For example:\r\n  - Right-click on a project → \"Add worktree\" → enter branch name\r\n  - Or via a slash command like \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree create <branch-name>\r\n\u001b[0m  - Delete worktree via right-click or \u001b[38;2;51;102;255m/worktree remove <path>\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[1mActual\u001b[0m \u001b[1mbehavior\r\n\u001b[0m  No context menu item, slash command, or button to add/remove worktrees. Users must use an external\r\n   terminal to run \u001b[38;2;51;102;255mgit worktree add\u001b[0m.\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mEnvironment\r\n\u001b[0m  - OS: Windows 11\r\n  - TermCanvas version: 0.25.15\r\n\u001b[93C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102m (°>   \r\n\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────      \u001b[38;2;102;102;102m||    \r\n\u001b[0m> \u001b[7m \u001b[89C\u001b[38;2;102;102;102;27m_(__)_  \r\n\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────     \u001b[38;2;102;102;102m^^^^   \r\n\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;102;102;102m? for shortcuts\u001b[74C\u001b[3mBiscuit\u001b[0m  \r\n\u001b[5A\u001b[96C\u001b[?2004h\u001b[?1004h",
                "sessionId": "2e3e51ce-7fd8-49e1-afc7-592003363178",
